data.title: Congratulations, Class of 2016!
data.text:
The ECU School of Dental Medicine is proud to have graduated the Class of 2016 on May 7. Listed here are the names of the graduates, their towns of origins in parentheses, and their immediate professional plans.

The school is also proud to list awards and honors earned by the graduates. We will miss these exceptional dentists and wish them every success in their future endeavors.
